metadata.name: The Last Step
metadata.description:
The last step is the first image from the "In Silence" series. 
This image was taken in Istanbul in 2019, just a few months before the Covid epidemic in the world.

The sound behind this image is the sound of the Bosphorus waves, seagulls and the whistles of ships. Sounds that can still be heard in the silence of the photo.
---

photo details:
Canon 5D mark III - 24/70 @70 mm - F/4 - 1/320 s - ISO 100
